(11, 'Lymphatic Drainage Massage', 'Lymphatic Drainage Massage Where You Need It', 'lymphatic-drainage-massage-in-london.webp', '<h2>What is Lymphatic Drainage Massage?</h2>\r\n<p>Our lymphatic drainage massage therapy aims to boost the functioning of your lymphatic system, which plays a vital role in immunity and detoxification.</p>\r\n<p>Blockages in this network can lead to fluid build up, causing oedema, fatigue, and increased susceptibility to illnesses like colds. By stimulating your lymph nodes through massage, you can clear these blockages, revitalise your system, eliminate toxins, and enhance your resistance to illness, ultimately strengthening your immunity.</p>\r\n<p>Experience some of the best lymphatic drainage massage London has on offer, including our lymphatic massage for face treatment, by understanding all the options available and then booking your next treatment with one of our Central London body massage treatment specialists!</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Massage in London - Therapist at Work\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/lymphatic-drainage-massage-london-therapist.webp\" alt=\"Professional therapist providing lymphatic drainage massage in London\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Lymphatic Massage for Face</h2>\r\n<p>Discover the rejuvenating power of our lymphatic facial massages. This highly specialised treatment not only enhances your complexion but can also aid in detoxification. It works by stimulating your lymph flow, to help flush out toxins and reduces facial puffiness, giving you a refreshed and youthful glow.</p>\r\n<p>A really popular choice amongst Londoners!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a style=\"background-color: #ff5609; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html\">Book A Lymphatic Massage for Face</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of a Lymphatic Drainage Massage</h2>\r\n<p>Our lymphatic fluid drainage massage is a gentle technique that stimulates the movement of lymph fluid through lymphatic vessels, benefiting your immune system and boosting blood circulation.</p>\r\n<p>Lymph fluid, derived from extracellular fluid, plays a crucial role in maintaining fluid balance, nutrient transport, waste removal, and immune support.</p>\r\n<p>During the session, your specially trained therapist will use specific strokes and massage techniques that promote lymphatic flow through your lymph vessels.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Enhance Overall Health &amp; Wellness</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Our specialised body massage targets the whole of your lymphatic system: lymph nodes, vessels, and organs, to create a harmonious balance within your body\'s internal environment that boosts detoxification.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Massage in London - Exploring the Lymphatic System\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/lymphatic-drainage-massage-london-lymphatic-system.webp\" alt=\"Anatomy of the lymphatic system - Understanding lymphatic drainage massage in London\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>In addition to reactivating your lymphatic drainage system, our manual lymphatic drainage massage in London offers a range of additional wellness benefits:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Enhance Sleep Quality</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By soothing your body and mind to a state of deep relaxation, this body massage technique can improve insomnia, helping you achieve a more restful and rejuvenating sleep.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Boost Vitality</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Through targeted stimulation, this specialised massage promotes increased vitality, leaving you with a renewed sense of energy and vigour.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Slow Ageing Process</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>The gentle yet effective techniques used by a manual lymphatic drainage massage therapist in London can help slow down the ageing process, reduce fine lines and promote healing for a more youthful complexion. Safer and cheaper than cosmetic surgery or liposuction!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Reduce Cellulite</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By targeting the lymphatic vessels and promoting detoxification, this style of massage and related treatment plan drains fluid that is in excess of requirements and can help remove cellulite tissue, leading to smoother and firmer skin.</p>\r\n<p>Experience these remarkable benefits by booking a manual lymphatic drainage massage session for your next treatment at home in London!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Lymphatic Drainage Massage: Understanding Its Role</h2>\r\n<p>Lymphatic drainage massage is a specialised technique performed to assist the body\'s natural process of draining excess fluid and bacteria.</p>\r\n<p>Often, after an injury or due to certain health conditions, patients may experience swelling or bloating, especially in areas like the abdomen.</p>\r\n<p>This massage targets these congested zones, working gently from the head down, to alleviate swelling and reduce bloating. By doing so, it can also address issues of congestion that sometimes manifest after prolonged illness or allergies.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>While it\'s undoubtedly beneficial for many, it\'s crucial to have a consultation before undergoing the treatment to ensure it\'s appropriate for the patient\'s unique needs and conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of Having a Lymphatic Drainage Massage at Home in London</h2>\r\n<p>When you\'re feeling unwell or experiencing symptoms of lymphedema, much like during a severe cold or fibromyalgia flare-up, the idea of travelling across London for manual lymphatic drainage massages, especially targeting the neck and other inflamed tissues, may not be appealing.</p>\r\n<p>That\'s where our mobile massage service comes into play!</p>\r\n<p>By choosing one of our mobile lymphatic drainage massage London therapists, you can relax in the comfort of your own home, feeling relaxed and free from the tension in muscles, while a professional therapist travels to you. These massages not only alleviate inflammation but also improve the appearance of swollen areas by promoting the movement of lymphatic fluids back into the bloodstream.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Massage in London - Leg Massage Technique\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/lymphatic-drainage-massage-london-leg-massage.webp\" alt=\"Relaxing lymphatic drainage massage on legs in London\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>Additionally, since multiple treatments typically yield the best results, opting for a home service saves you from the hassle of repeated trips to a clinic, making it an even more compelling reason to book one of our convenient at-home lymphatic drainage massages in London.</p>\r\n<p>Our experienced massage therapists can organise a treatment plan based on your medical history and taking into account any chronic conditions, ensuring the optimal health of your lymphocytes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Our Range of Lymphatic Massage Treatments in London</h2>\r\n<p>At The Massage Rooms, we pride ourselves on offering a wide range of lymphatic drainage massage therapies to cater to the diverse needs of our clients.</p>\r\n<p>Our most popular styles in this therapy type include Manual Lymphatic Drainage (MLD) together with other massage treatments such as sports massage, deep tissue massage, and lymphatic drainage facial treatments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>MLD massage</h3>\r\n<p>As practised by our lymphatic drainage massage experts and <a title=\"Physio Lymphatic Drainage Methods\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/physio_style_massage\">physio-style</a> therapists, MLD treatment employs gentle techniques to target the lymph nodes, enhancing the body\'s natural healing and detoxification processes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Sports Massage</h3>\r\n<p><a title=\"Lymphatic Drainage often used during Sports Massage\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/sports_massage\">Sports massages</a> are ideal for athletes, providing pain relief and performance improvement through targeted deep-tissue massage techniques.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Deep Tissue Massage</h3>\r\n<p><a title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Therapy through Deep Tissue Techniques\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/deep_tissue_massage\">Deep tissue massages</a> are available for individuals seeking tension reduction, pain relief, and improved muscle flexibility.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Massage in London - Facial Swelling Reduction Results\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/ lymphatic-drainage-massage-london-facial-swelling.webp\" alt=\"Facial swelling reduction achieved through lymphatic drainage massage in London\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>Amongst the many benefits of gentle form MLD therapy, the ability to reduce swelling, rid the body of waste products and deal with ailments commonly associated with conditions such as <a title=\"Learn more about how massage can be used to treat Fibromyalgia pain\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/treating-fibromyalgia-pain-with-massage\">fibromyalgia</a> stand out. It is also believed that the removal of excess fluid associated with lymphatic treatments can help in reducing swelling often suffered by those with rheumatoid arthritis conditions.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Additionally, our sought-after lymphatic drainage facial treatments stimulate the lymphatic system, promoting detoxification, reducing puffiness, enhancing circulation, and revealing a rejuvenated, radiant complexion.</p>\r\n<p>With our skilled practitioners able to come to you for your comfort, we believe we have offer one of the most convenient and effective solutions tailored to your individual needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Post Lymphatic System Massage:&nbsp;How You\'ll Feel After A Treatment</h2>\r\n<p>After a lymphatic massage, most people experience a significant improvement in their well-being. This highly specialised and gentle form technique invigorates and relaxes, leaving you with a sense of rejuvenation.</p>\r\n<p>Many clients report feeling as if their body has efficiently released toxins, granting a newfound freshness. However, each person\'s experience is unique.</p>\r\n<p>Once the massage concludes, you\'ll notice a lightness, heightened energy, and a glowing complexion. For Londoners, this body massage therapy style has become increasingly popular in recent years, serving as an effective stress management tool, eliminating dead skin cells and toxins, and enhancing overall skin condition.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>If you looking for a safe and natural relaxing massage with added health and wellness benefits, lymphatic massage therapy can prove to be an ideal treatment choice.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How does light pressure massage reduce fluid retention?</h2>\r\n<p>This highly unique massage technique is delivered by specially trained mobile therapists who primarily focus on enhancing lymph flow. Doing so plays a critical role in flushing out excess fluids and toxins from your body.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By employing specific lymph drainage techniques, with delicate pressure, our skilled therapists promote healing by supporting your body\'s natural immune function and reducing water retention.</p>\r\n<p>Many of our upper body treatments incorporate light pressure. So a lymphatic drainage massage is also a fantastic complement to treatments like sports massage, that also target specific areas of tension. By easing excess lymphatic fluid levels and giving your immune system a boost, a full lymphatic flow drainage session can also be a highly relaxing massage that improves overall well-being, and leaves you feeling totally refreshed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Does Lymphatic Massage Aid Weight Loss?</h2>\r\n<p>Lymphatic massage is often used an alternative fat reduction therapy and is offered across London spas and specialist centres - and now in the comfort of your own home through us!</p>\r\n<p>The weight loss concept is based on the belief that stimulating lymphatic drainage can break down fat deposits, boost metabolism, improve circulation and contribute to weight reduction.</p>\r\n<p>While some evidence suggests potential benefits in weight management, most studies have not yet conclusively established this form of therapy as an effective weight-loss solution.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>We advise you use this massage therapy in conjunction with a range of slimming techniques.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How Long Does It Take for Lymphatic Drainage to Show Results?</h2>\r\n<p>The effectiveness of lymphatic drainage can vary based on individual health conditions and how deep layers of the lymphatic system are affected. Generally, you may notice reduced swelling after your initial session at home in London, especially in certain areas like the lower limbs.</p>\r\n<p>To fully experience the full range of benefits, which can include reduce stress, multiple sessions lasting 30 to 60 minutes each are recommended. During these sessions, therapists focus on applying pressure in specific ways to stimulate lymphatic tissue and the immune system.</p>\r\n<p>The number of sessions required depends on the severity of your condition, medical history, and any specific areas that need more intensive care. It is best to discuss your condition with one of our specialist therapists for more personalised advice.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Lymphatic drainage necessitates ongoing dedication for long-term results, as it is not a quick fix. Another good reason to use our mobile service for your next manual lymphatic drainage massage appointment to get it in the comfort of your own home!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Discover London\'s Top Lymphatic Drainage Massage Therapists</h2>\r\n<p>Our trained therapists offer mobile Lymphatic Drainage Massages in London, bringing deep relaxation to your doorstep. Fast arrival - within an hour!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>[[BOOKING]]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Pregnant or Just Given Birth?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our Pregnancy massages in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/pregnancy_massage\">Explore Pregnancy Massages</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2017-06-29 21:30:09', '2025-09-11 23:32:21', '<p>A gentle, rhythmic type of massage that can help stimulate lymph flow and reduce fluid retention.</p>', '<p><a title=\"5-star rated therapists\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/Feedback/Feedback.html\">Top-rated Therapists</a></p>\r\n<p>Home and hotel visits</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Only &pound;59</strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 'Book Lymphatic Drainage', 'https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html', 'What is a lymphatic drainage massage?', 'What are the benefits of lymphatic drainage massage?', '<p><br />As well as promoting the reactivation of your lymphatic drainage system, this massage can also help:<br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Improve insomnia<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Increase your vitality<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Slow down the ageing process<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Remove cellulite tissue<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>Why you should get your Lymphatic Drainage massage at home rather than at a clinic</h3>\r\n<p><br />A lymphatic drainage massage is often needed when we feel down, similar to a heavy&nbsp;cold. Consequently, travelling around London is not an attractive proposition, at that time.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/visiting/what-is-mobile-massage-in-london\">mobile massage in London</a>&nbsp;allows you to continue to relax while your professional therapist&nbsp;travels to your place instead. Furthermore, this treatment usually has the best results as a series of treatments - even more reason to book an outcall service and avoid the repeated trips to a clinic.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Lymphatic Drainage Massage | Delivered from £59 | TheMassageRooms', 'Receive a lymphatic drainage massage at your location in London. Book a mobile therapist near you to improve circulation on demand.', 'lymphatic_drainage_massage', 'Lymphatic drainage massage therapist in London working on client\'s thighs', 'Lymphatic Drainage Massage in London: Strengthening Your Immune System at Home', NULL),
(12, 'Pregnancy Massage', 'Pregnancy Massage In Your Own Home', 'pre-natal-pregnancy-massage-in-london.webp', '<h2>Pregnancy Massage Made Easy: Book Now, Relax at Home!</h2>\r\n<p>Struggling to find a convenient pregnancy massage near you? We take the stress out of it! Our professional, qualified therapists come directly to your home, allowing you to enjoy spa-quality relaxation without leaving your comfort zone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Find Pregnancy Massage Therapists Near You\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html\">Find a Pregnancy Massage Therapist Near You Now</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Is Pregnancy Massage Safe?</h2>\r\n<p>Yes, massage is generally safe after the first trimester (12+ weeks), but always consult your doctor before booking.</p>\r\n<p>For a complete breakdown of safety considerations during pregnancy massage, visit our dedicated guide: <strong><a title=\"Pregnancy Massage: Safety Considerations\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/is-massage-safe-during-pregnancy\">Pregnancy Massage: Safety Considerations</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Here at The Massage Rooms, we offer treatments with the utmost comfort and hygiene in mind. We use your own towels and conduct massages on your bed or chair (thereby avoiding shared tables).</p>\r\n<p>For optimal comfort, consider using a pregnancy pillow or cushions during your massage.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Pregnancy Massage: Upper Back Body Massage is Popular\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/upper-back-pregnancy-massage.webp\" alt=\"Pregnant woman getting upper back pregnancy massage in London\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Discover the Benefits of Pregnancy Massages</h2>\r\n<p>Our selection of prenatal and general maternity treatments offer a multitude of benefits for your body and your mind.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f0f0; text-align: center; margin: 20px; padding: 20px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Our skilled therapists use soft and soothing methods to help:</h3>\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;\">\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➊</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Relieve tension, pain, and muscle aches</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➋</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Calm you down and improve your sleep</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➌</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Alleviate backache without medication</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➍</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Reduce water retention and boost your energy levels</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➎</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Relieve morning sickness and nausea symptoms</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➏</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Reduce stress levels and enhance your mood</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"benefit\" style=\"flex: 0 1 300px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; color: #fc3c0b; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px;\">➐</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #333;\">Improve circulation and reduce pregnancy stretch marks</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;\">To enjoy these benefits with our professional prenatal massage therapists, simply book your appointment today!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>The Benefits of a Home Treatment</h3>\r\n<p>If you think you have to travel to a spa for a wonderful soothing session, think again! You\'ll enjoy a completely serene and calming atmosphere as our practitioners work their magic during your pregnancy massage treatment at home in London.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>Saving you the time and trouble of travelling, we\'ll turn your favourite room at home into a dedicated treatment room just for you.</p>\r\n<p>The gentle yet effective touch of our therapists will be primarily focused on your optimum convenience and help you ease tension. You\'ll feel the soothing sensations as they employ various procedures, such as gentle yoga-inspired stretches, rhythmic movements, and the use of essential oils.</p>\r\n<p>Our specialists can focus on specific areas of discomfort, providing targeted relief where needed to help with a range of common pregnancy symptoms, such as liquid retention and swelling in ankles &amp; feet.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>A duration of one hour is usually sufficient and ensures you feel comfortable throughout.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep pregnancy related tension to a minimum by turning your home into a treatment room haven for a few hours, simply by booking a regular pregnancy massage with one of our empathetic specialists. Enjoy the luxuries of a Bamford pregnancy massage without having to leave your home and travel to the treatment rooms of a Bamford wellness spa or the Berkeley Health club spa near busy Hyde Park Corner.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>Book now and our specialist could be at yours within the hour!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Our Prenatal, Antenatal and Postnatal Treatments: We Nurture Mothers at Every Stage</h2>\r\n<p>Pregnancy is a transformative journey with distinct stages that require specific care and attention. Our range of massage for pregnancy (pre-natal, antenatal, and postnatal treatment) are all tailored to maternity needs and cater to the evolving demands of expectant and new mothers.</p>\r\n<p>Let\'s explore the various massage types and techniques and how they provide nurturing support throughout different stages of motherhood.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>Our maternity treatments generally focus on the muscles around your legs, feet, neck and shoulders. Any massage around the abdomen area is performed in a very soft and relaxing manner. Our pregnancy therapies are performed without the use of aromatherapy essential oils to avoid the risk of adverse reactions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Pre-Natal Massage: Supporting Expectant Mothers</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #ff840c;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Prenatal Massage for Pregnant Women\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/pre-natal-pregnancy-massage.webp\" alt=\"Prenatal massage for pregnant women\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></span></span>➪ </strong></span></span>Pre-natal massages are tailored to the unique needs of expecting mothers. These sessions focus on addressing physical body and mental emotional changes during pregnancy, offering tranquillity and relief from common discomforts such as fluid retention.</p>\r\n<p>Our skilled therapists use gentle techniques, such as scalp massage with hot towels wrapped around your head, to ensure safety for baby and optimum comfort for mother. Our prenatal pregnancy massage is specifically designed to promote calmness, reduce aches, improve circulation and can alleviate pregnancy-related tension.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Antenatal Massage: Preparing for Birth</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Antenatal Massage: Aid Relaxation Just Before Birth\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/ante-natal-pregnancy-massage.webp\" alt=\"Antenatal Massage to aid relaxation just before giving birth\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" />➪ </strong></span></span>Ante-natal massages, often used interchangeably with pre-natal massages, can also specifically refer to a pregnancy massage received in the third trimester (week 25 onwards), just before childbirth. They provide support as expectant mothers prepare for the birthing process.</p>\r\n<p>Antenatal treatments address the physical effects of pregnancy and enhance peacefulness, reducing anxiety and preparing the body for labour. Therapists create a nurturing environment, applying gentle methods to support your wellbeing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Postnatal Massage: Supporting New Mothers</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Postnatal Massage: Specifically Designed To Relieve Post Birth Tension\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/post-natal-pregnancy-massage.webp\" alt=\"Postnatal Massage relieving tension after birth\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" />➪ </strong></span></span>Postnatal massage focuses on the recovery and well-being of new mothers after childbirth. This form of full body massage helps with physical body as well as mental challenges during the postpartum period.</p>\r\n<p>Our practitioners aim to support the body\'s healing process, restore muscle tone, and alleviate aches and pains. A postnatal pregnancy massage employs techniques like lymphatic drainage to help reduce muscle tension, inspire relaxation, and contribute to stress reduction and hormonal balance, aiding in overall rejuvenation as mothers transition into their new role. We also offer <a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/massage-assisted-stretching\">assisted-stretching based massages</a> which can help with reducing the appearance of pregnancy stretch marks.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Tailoring the Massage to Your Needs</h2>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re seeking pre-natal, ante-natal, or a full body postnatal massage for pregnancy, it\'s very important to effectively communicate your concerns and requirements to your personal masseuse. Our skilled practitioners will adapt the style and provide bespoke care to ensure your peace of mind and address your individual needs at each stage of your pregnancy journey.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>We believe an open communication channel leads to the best massages.</p>\r\n<p>Treatments can cover the full body or just focus on a few specific tense areas, according to your preferences and comfort level. Our primary aim is to ensure a peaceful pregnancy massage for you and your developing baby.</p>\r\n<p>Popular and highly regarded options for this style encompass indulgent facial massage and scalp massage, a rejuvenating foot soak followed by foot massage at revitalising pressure points for tired and swollen feet, and other specialised methods to address concerns such as stretch marks.</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, our therapies may include <a title=\"Lymphatic Drainage Techniques in Pregnancy Massage Therapy\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/lymphatic_drainage_massage\">lymphatic drainage</a> to promote fluid balance and targeted attention to the upper and lower back to relieve tension and enhance overall serenity.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>Experience nurturing support and calmness throughout your motherhood journey - enter your address in the search box at bottom of this page to find appropriately qualified therapists near you in London!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>A Perfect Treat for Mums-to-Be in London</h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Prenatal Pregnancy Massage Benefits: Restore Calm and Alleviate Stress\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/newborn-baby.webp\" alt=\"Image of a newborn baby sleeping calmly\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" />We understand the importance of offering a tranquil oasis for mums-to-be in London. Our best pregnancy massages are the perfect treat to nurture your body and mind, providing a moment of total relaxation and rejuvenation.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span></span>Whether you\'re at the beginning of your second trimester or at the end of your pregnancy journey in your third trimester ... or have even recently given birth ... our service providers are here to ensure you receive the care and attention you deserve.</p>\r\n<p>Our aim is to provide relief for expectant mums with a gentle, full-body massage experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Book Bliss with a Pregnancy Massage Today</h2>\r\n<p>If you\'re past your third trimester, don\'t miss the opportunity to experience the blissful benefits of a pregnancy massage in London today.</p>\r\n<p>Book a peaceful and beneficial pregnancy massage in the convenience of your home in London. We provide a seamless booking experience and quickly connect you with qualified pregnancy massage therapists in your area. Just enter your postcode below to find your nearest specialists:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Find Pregnancy Massage Therapists Near You\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html\">Find a Pregnancy Massage Therapist in London</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Take the first step towards relaxation and wellness by using our user-friendly online booking system to find some of London\'s best qualified pregnancy massage specialists.</p>\r\n<p>Indulge in the ultimate self-care experience and let one of our skilled therapists create a tranquil haven for at least 60 minutes in the comfort of your own home!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Seeking Body Sculpting?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our anti-cellulite Slimming massage in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/slimming_massage\">Consider Anti-Cellulite Slimming Massage</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2017-06-29 21:31:37', '2025-09-11 23:33:53', '<p>A soft, nurturing massage tailored for prenatal or postnatal care to help mothers relax and rejuvenate.</p>', NULL, 1, 1, 'Book a Pregnancy Massage', 'https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html', 'What is a pregnancy massage?', 'What are the benefits of pregnancy massage?', '<p><br />As well as the most simple benefit of just feeling &lsquo;treated&rsquo; during your pregnancy, our pre-natal massage can also help:<br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Reduce&nbsp;swelling around&nbsp;ankles;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>regulate&nbsp;the hormones which control your stress levels;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>ease&nbsp;back aches&nbsp;without resorting to medication;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>stabilise&nbsp;blood pressure;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>rejuvenate&nbsp;mood; and&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>improve&nbsp;the quality of sleep.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Why a home visit Pregnancy massage is better</h3>\r\n<p><br />During the second and third trimesters of&nbsp;pregnancy, mobility levels are reduced and travelling becomes increasingly more of a pain. Book a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/visiting/what-is-mobile-massage-in-london\">mobile massage&nbsp;in London</a> instead to save yourself the bother of extra journeys and enjoy your relaxation treatment in the comfort of your own home.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Pregnancy Massage | At Home for £59 | TheMassageRooms', 'Enjoy a relaxing pre-natal or post-natal pregnancy massage in the comfort of your home in London. Book a mobile therapist to care for you at any stage, anywhere in the city.', 'pregnancy_massage', 'Pregnancy massage specialist performing a prenatal treatment on a pregnant woman', 'Prenatal Pregnancy Massage in London: A Soothing Treatment for Mothers To Be', NULL),
(13, 'Slimming Massage', 'Anti-Cellulite Slimming Massage Direct to You', 'slimming-anti-cellulite-massage-in-london.webp', '<h2>What is a slimming massage?</h2>\r\n<p>Anti-cellulite massage, also known as slimming massage, is a highly effective method to reduce cellulite and promote fat reduction.</p>\r\n<p>This specialised massage technique aims to loosen fatty tissues beneath the skin and visibly smooth its surface. Our therapists employ manual techniques tailored to your unique body type, rather than relying on generic electronic machines.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of Anti-Cellulite Slimming Massage</h2>\r\n<h3><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Cellulite Treatment For Thighs: A Popular Treated Area in Slimming Massages\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/cellulite-therapy-on-thighs.webp\" alt=\"Cellulite treatment works well on female body areas such as thighs\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" />Reduce cellulite</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Regular anti-cellulite slimming massages, combined with a balanced diet and regular exercise, can effectively reduce the appearance of cellulite, particularly in areas such as the thighs and buttocks.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Smooth skin appearance</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Our specialised treatment targets fat cells and stimulate blood circulation, helping to smooth the appearance of the skin and improve its texture.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Boost confidence and self-esteem</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By promoting cellulite reduction and enhancing the overall appearance of your skin, our slimming massage treatments can significantly improve your confidence and self-esteem.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Stay motivated in your weight loss journey</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>In conjunction with a weight loss program, our anti-cellulite slimming massages can serve as a motivating factor, encouraging you to stay dedicated to your goals of body sculpting and cellulite reduction.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>While this type of massage can positively impact the normal ageing process by boosting collagen production and improving the health of connective tissues, it\'s vital to maintain realistic expectations. Just chat with our professional for more personalised advice.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>What To Expect During Your Slimming Massage Session</h2>\r\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" title=\"Cellulite Treatment London: Targeting Cellulite Beneath Skin\'s Surface\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/anti-cellulite-treatment-stomach.webp\" alt=\"Slimming massage therapist targeting client\'s cellulite beneath skin\'s surface\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" />During your slimming massage session, our skilled therapist will apply firm circular motions to specifically target underlying fatty tissues, providing an effective cellulite reduction treatment.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>These techniques are performed with empathy and care, considering your comfort throughout the treatment.</p>\r\n<p>To further enhance the elasticity of your skin and diminish the appearance of cellulite dimples, our therapists may also incorporate gentle skin pinching and stretching motions.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By applying these techniques, the connective tissue is stimulated, promoting a smoother skin surface and reducing the visibility of cellulite.</p>\r\n<p>While slimming massages can involve vigorous movements and occasional discomfort, your well-being is our priority.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>If you ever experience any discomfort during the session, please communicate openly with your therapist. They will make the necessary adjustments to ensure your continued comfort and provide you with the most effective treatment possible.</p>\r\n<p>Finally, our therapists also incorporate lymphatic drainage techniques into your massage to further accelerate cellulite removal.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By <a title=\"Learn about our sister treatment, Lymphatic Drainage massages in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/lymphatic_drainage_massage\">stimulating your lymphatic system</a>, helping to eliminate toxins and reduce fluid retention, which can contribute to the appearance of cellulite.</p>\r\n<p>Slimming massages are a very popular maths of reducing cellulite, targeting fatty deposits that commonly affect most women, especially in areas such as the inner thighs.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>With regular sessions, you can expect to see a noticeably reduced appearance of cellulite, ultimately improving the overall appearance and texture of your skin.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Getting Anti-Cellulite Slimming Treatments at Home vs Beauty Spa</h2>\r\n<p>When considering anti-cellulite slimming treatments, you have the option of receiving them at a beauty spa or in the comfort of your own home with us.</p>\r\n<p>Beauty spas in London offer a range of cellulite treatments, including full body massages, acoustic wave therapy, laser treatments, and radio frequency sessions. These settings can provide access to specialised equipment and therapists who can deliver treatments targeting orange peel skin and water retention.</p>\r\n<p>However, opting for at-home cellulite massage can also target the same issues and offers some additional advantages. Not only can you enjoy the convenience and privacy of your own space, but you can also tailor the sessions to fit your schedule.</p>\r\n<p>We believe receiving your treatments at home with one of our specialists does not compromise on the quality or effectiveness of slimming therapy sessions.</p>\r\n<p>In fact, with the proper guidance of one of our skilled and empathetic practitioners, you could achieve the best results without the need to travel, making our at-home slimming massage in London more convenient and beneficial.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Our therapists bring their expertise right to the comfort of your own surroundings in London, so booking with us will get you an at-home anti-cellulite massage experience!</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Our aim is to provide you with a noticeable reduction in cellulite and improved skin laxity, without the privacy and travel concerns often associated with visiting a spa for anti-cellulite treatments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Book an Anti-Cellulite Slimming Massage in London</h2>\r\n<p>Find your nearest slimming massage therapists simply by entering your postcode below:</p>\r\n<p>[[BOOKING]]</p>\r\n<p>Our experienced therapists provide mobile Anti-Cellulite Slimming Massage services, so you\'ll enjoy the benefits at your own home or hotel room in London. Experience the power of this targeted massage in as little as one hour!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Prefer Some Acupressure?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our Shiatsu massage in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/shiatsu-massage\">Try a Shiatsu Massage</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2017-06-29 21:32:54', '2025-09-11 23:34:56', '<p>A firm pressure, body sculpting massage using short, rapid strokes and deep kneading to target cellulite.</p>', '<p><a title=\"5-star rated therapists\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/Feedback/Feedback.html\">Top-rated Therapists</a></p>\r\n<p>Home and hotel visits</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Only &pound;59</strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 'Book a Slimming Massage', 'https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html', 'What is a slimming massage?', 'What are the benefits of an anti-cellulite massage?', '<p><br />A course of these anti-cellulite&nbsp;massages, together with a balanced&nbsp;diet and regular exercise, can help:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Reduce cellulite, especially around your thighs and buttocks;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>smooth the appearance of skin;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>improve your confidence and self-esteem; and<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>keep you motivated to&nbsp;continue with&nbsp;a&nbsp;weight loss programme</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Slimming Anti-Cellulite Massages | At Your Place | TheMassageRooms', 'Enjoy an effective anti-cellulite slimming massage at your home or hotel in London. Book a mobile therapist near you for targeted toning and smoother skin, wherever you are in the city.', 'slimming_massage', 'Qualified therapist performing Slimming Anti-Cellulite Belly massage in London', 'Slimming Anti-Cellulite Massage London: Reducing Fat around the Belly', NULL);
