(15, 'Office Massage', 'Office Massage: We Can Set Up Anywhere!', 'office-massage-in-london.webp', '<h2>What is an Office Massage in London?</h2>\r\n<p>Our office massages in London are rejuvenating corporate massage services that can help transform your workplace into a stress-free and revitalising environment for your employees and other stakeholder!</p>\r\n<p>Our team of expert massage therapists specialise in on-site chair massages, providing relief and improved morale to worked in your London offices, outlets and during corporate events.</p>\r\n<p>We understand the challenges of a busy city like London, where workplace stress can lead to decreased productivity and employee morale. That\'s why we bring the relaxation and therapeutic benefits of our London office massage directly to your workspace, allowing employees to experience the wonders of stress relief and enhanced well-being without leaving the office.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of Corporate Massages in London</h2>\r\n<p>The benefits of our office massage service in London are enormous, addressing the pressing issues faced by employees in the modern work environment.</p>\r\n<p>Offering corporate massages on-site comes with a plethora of advantages, such as:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Stress Relief</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Office massage sessions help reduce workplace stress, promoting a calmer and more focused atmosphere for employees.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Enhanced Morale</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>A complimentary 10-minute head, neck, and shoulder on-site chair massage can provide a quick escape for employees, boosting their morale, focus and overall job satisfaction.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Improved Posture</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>A regular chair massage at employees\' desks encourage better posture, reducing the risk of work-related injuries and discomfort.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Reduced Absenteeism</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>By investing in the mental health and wellbeing of your staff through on-site chair massages, you can help reduce absenteeism and improve staff retention.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Boosted Immune Systems</strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Office based therapy is known to reduce anxiety and contribute to improved immune systems, leading to healthier and more resilient employees.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How our Corporate Massages in London are Performed</h2>\r\n<p>Our highly skilled massage therapists perform office massages in London with the utmost professionalism and care.</p>\r\n<p>We will despatch a qualified and experienced massage therapist directly to your workplace, eliminating the need for employees to leave the office, ensuring convenience and minimal disruption to their work schedules. Our on-site chair massages target specific areas of tension, providing effective relief and relaxation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you have a large number of employees receiving the benefit we can organise more than one massage therapist to visit concurrently.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Whether it\'s a 10-minute head, neck, and shoulder massage or a customised massage session, we employ various massage techniques, from <a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/jet_lag_hangover_massage\">Indian head massage</a> to <a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/foot-reflexology-massage\">Foot reflexology massage</a> treatments, to cater to individual needs and preferences.</p>\r\n<p>Even a simple 5-minute shoulder, hand and arm massage can help prevent the onset of common workplace injuries and conditions such as <a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/repetitive_strain_injury\">repetitive strain injury</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The massage sessions are conducted in a quiet room or designated area, ensuring a stress-free experience for employees, allowing them to recharge and return to work feeling refreshed and invigorated.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>A Selection of our Workplace Massage Clients</h2>\r\n<p>We provide our corporate massage services to a wide range of successful businesses and organisations in London of all shapes and sizes as well as at special events and trade shows.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Corporate Massage Services: A Selection of Companies we are providing office massage for\" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/office-massage-london-clients.webp\" alt=\"Logos of our corporate clients for on site chair massage services\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Book an Office Massage in London</h2>\r\n<p>Take the first step towards a healthier, happier, and more productive workplace by scheduling regular massages in London. Contact us now to discuss your specific requirements and witness the positive impact our massages can bring to your business.</p>\r\n<p>Ready to boost employee morale and wellness at your London firm?</p>\r\n<p>Book a corporate massage with The Massage Rooms in London today and let our skilled massage therapists provide the rejuvenating experience your employees deserve!</p>\r\n<p>We offer a variety of massage services, from on-site chair massage to bespoke packages of treatments specifically tailored to suit your office working environment or special events. Show your appreciation to employees and attract a crowd at corporate events with our relaxing chair massages.</p>\r\n<p>To discuss your particular requirements, please&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:admin@themassagerooms.com?subject=Office%20Massage%20Enquiry\">e-mail us</a>&nbsp;and we will get back to you within 24 hours and often the very&nbsp;same day.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Want A More Relaxing Massage?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our Swedish massage in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/classic_swedish_massage\">Explore Classic Swedish Massage</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2017-06-29 21:34:34', '2025-09-11 23:33:04', '<p>Chair massage focusing on relieving tension and stress in the workplace or during events.</p>', '<p>Boost Employee Morale!</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"5-star rated therapists\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/Feedback/Feedback.html\">Top-rated Therapists</a></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>From Only &pound;59</strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 'Make an Enquiry', 'mailto:admin@themassagerooms.com?subject=Office%20Massage%20Enquiry', 'What is an office massage?', 'What are the benefits of an office or event massage?', '<p><br />Stress in the workplace is at an all-time high all around the world and especially so in busy cities like London. For employers&nbsp;this can result in unpredictable resourcing. Stress lowers employee morale and often has a consequential increase in&nbsp;the number of&nbsp;sick days taken by staff.</p>\r\n<p><br />Employee perk schemes such as regular on-site office massages can do wonders to restore morale and boost happiness and loyalty towards employers.&nbsp;Chair-based office&nbsp;massages have a multitude of widely accepted <a href=\"https://www.incorporatemassage.com/blog/benefits-of-chair-massage\">benefits</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />So whether you are considering booking a massage therapist to attend an&nbsp;annual&nbsp;corporate event such as a Christmas party,&nbsp;a&nbsp;trade exhibition for impressing customers and suppliers or as a more regular perk&nbsp;to boost office&nbsp;employee morale,&nbsp;our on-site massage treatments are an excellent and affordable way to improve employee happiness and give your&nbsp;business a welcome boost!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Office Massages | At Your Desk Today | TheMassageRooms', 'Boost employee morale & productivity with our chair massage at your offices in London. Book a mobile therapist for a quick stress relief session anywhere in the city.', 'office_massage', 'Woman receiving an office chair massage in London at work', 'Office Massage in London: Improve Employee Morale & Reduce Stress', NULL),
(16, 'Shiatsu Massage', 'Shiatsu Massage Right To Your Door', 'shiatsu-massage-in-london.webp', '<h2>What is Shiatsu Massage?</h2>\r\n<p>Originating in Japan and gaining popularity over the last 40 years, Shiatsu massage is a practice that involves applying medium pressure using the soft tips of your therapist\'s fingers to specific pressure points (known as \'acupoints\') on your body. This therapeutic technique can be combined with other massage styles, offering a unique and tailored experience.</p>\r\n<p>As part of our home massage service, we have therapists who are well-versed in Shiatsu and can incorporate it into any other treatment style they offer. By understanding the principles of Qi (vital energy) and the harmonious balance of Yin and Yang, our therapists aim to restore equilibrium and promote natural healing within your body.</p>\r\n<p>Shiatsu massage is one of a number of popular styles of <a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/most-popular-types-of-asian-massage\">Asian massages we offer in London</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How is Shiatsu Massage Performed?</h2>\r\n<p>During a typical Shiatsu massage session, your qualified therapist will use their knowledge of the human body\'s acupressure points and meridian lines to provide a deeply therapeutic experience. Your therapist will apply finger pressure using the soft tips of their fingers, palms, and thumbs to specific acupoints on your body.</p>\r\n<p>The pressure is applied calmly and steadily, and will specifically target areas that may be holding increased tension or experiencing discomfort. By working with these acupoints, your therapist will seek to release blockages, promote energy flow, and restore overall balance within your body.</p>\r\n<p>The techniques used in Shiatsu massage therapy can help alleviate chronic unease, provide relief, reduce work-related stress, and contribute to maintaining optimal physical and mental well-being.</p>\r\n<p>In London, our Shiatsu therapists also often integrate <strong><a href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/blog/post/myofascial-release-therapy\">Myofascial Release Therapy</a></strong>&nbsp;techniques alongside acupressure and stretches to create a holistic treatment plan for muscle tension and pain relief.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of Shiatsu Massage</h2>\r\n<p>Shiatsu massage, rooted in Eastern medicine, offers a wide range of benefits that can enhance your overall sense of wellness. Here are some of the benefits commonly associated with this style of medicinal massage:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Restoring Overall Energy</h3>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #f86a00;\">➪ </span></strong>Shiatsu massage can help restore vitality and is especially helpful if you\'ve been experiencing fatigue or a lack of energy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Reducing Tension, Stress, Anxiety, and Depression</h3>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #f86a00;\">➪ </span></strong>By targeting specific acupressure points and applying finger pressure, Shiatsu massage can effectively reduce tension, alleviate stress, and provide relief from anxiety and depression.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Improving Blood Circulation</h3>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #f86a00;\">➪ </span></strong>Shiatsu massage techniques improve blood circulation, promoting better overall blood flow throughout the body.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Relieving Common Discomforts</h3>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #f86a00;\">➪ </span></strong>Shiatsu massage can alleviate discomforts such as stiff neck, backaches, and sciatica, providing relief from chronic pain.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Enhancing Sleep Quality</h3>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #f86a00;\">➪ </span></strong>By promoting relaxation and reducing stress, Shiatsu massage can contribute to better sleep patterns and improve sleep quality.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Book A Shiatsu Massage Now</h3>\r\n<p>Target your acupuncture points to enjoy a more harmonious state of mind and body by booking your Shiatsu massage in London with us today:</p>\r\n<p>[[BOOKING]]</p>\r\n<p>Our London massage services are designed to help you find a locally based, tried and tested, professional shiatsu therapist who can visit you at your home or hotel room in a jiffy!</p>\r\n<p>Same day and last minute appointments are no problem, so don\'t stress about planning well in advance.</p>\r\n<p>To maintain optimum health in a central London environment, we recommend you aim to book shiatsu sessions around once a month.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Prefer Essential Oils in Your Treatment?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our Aromatherapy massages in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/aromatherapy-massage\">Explore Aromatherapy Massage Options</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2018-06-18 13:03:38', '2025-09-11 23:34:22', '<p>Japanese acupressure massage using finger pressure along meridian lines to restore energy balance.</p>', '<p><a title=\"5-star rated therapists\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/Feedback/Feedback.html\">Top-rated Therapists</a></p>\r\n<p>Home and hotel visits</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Only &pound;59</strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 'Book a Shiatsu Massage', 'https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html', 'What is Shiatsu massage?', 'What is Shiatsu massage good for?', '<p><br />Because of their background in Eastern medicine, Shiatsu massage&nbsp;(and acupressure generally) is&nbsp;believed to have a very wide range of benefits. Some of those often mentioned include:<br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Restoring&nbsp;overall energy, especially helpful if you have been&nbsp;suffering from fatigue;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>helpful in reducing&nbsp;overall tension, stress as well as anxiety and depression;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>improved blood circulation;<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>reduces common problem such as&nbsp;stiff neck and&nbsp;backaches, including sciatica; and<br />&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>can help aid better sleep.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Shiatsu Massage | Delivered Today for £59 | TheMassageRooms', 'Experience a shiatsu massage in the comfort of your own space. Book a mobile therapist in London for healing acupressure wherever you are.', 'shiatsu-massage', 'Thumb Pressure Being Applied During A Shiatsu Massage in London', 'Shiatsu Massage in London: Bringing Professional Asian Therapies To You At Home', NULL),
(17, 'Aromatherapy Massage', 'Aromatherapy Massage Right Where You Are', 'aromatherapy-massage-in-london.webp', '<p>Inspired by the art of blending essential oils with classical massage techniques, our skilled aromatherapy therapists are dedicated to bringing the therapeutic qualities of this soothing all-round treatment directly to your home or hotel room.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits of Aromatherapy Massage</h2>\r\n<p>Immerse yourself in serenity with our Aromatherapy Massage treatment in London. Our home visit therapists will create a harmonious fusion between scent and touch to maximise relaxation and improve your overall sense of well-being.</p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;termsAssistantParagraphWrapper&quot;,{&quot;isSelected&quot;:false,&quot;term&quot;:&quot;services&quot;}]\">Our aromatherapy massage services can be included as part of a complementary style such as Swedish massage or Deep Tissue massage.</p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;termsAssistantParagraphWrapper&quot;,{&quot;isSelected&quot;:false,&quot;term&quot;:&quot;services&quot;}]\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Relaxation and Emotional Balance</h3>\r\n<p>Feel emotionally relaxed as our empathy filled therapist harnesses the power and benefits of aromatherapy massage with essential oils to meet your individual needs, at your place.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>A gentle touch and aromatic scents will help release stress and a create a prevailing sense of calm.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Muscle Tension Relief</h3>\r\n<p>Ease muscle tension with the skilful techniques and psychological benefits of therapeutic massage oils brought to you by our specialists.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Enjoy a deeper sense of physical relaxation from head to toe, as you float away to soothing scents.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Improved Blood Circulation</h3>\r\n<p>Invigorating essential oils, selected for your specific health needs, can help promote blood circulation, delivering more oxygen and nutrients to your internal organs.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Relax your body with a bespoke aromatherapy massage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Boosted Immune System</h3>\r\n<p>Nurture your body\'s natural defence system for improved holistic wellness with our aromatherapy massages in London.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Revitalise your body with a bespoke aromatherapy massage. The immune-strengthening properties of essential oils can help prevent common ailments, such as colds, by improve your lymphatic system.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How Does Aromatherapy Massage Work?</h2>\r\n<p>Our aromatherapy massage therapists in London apply the following techniques during your treatment:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Effleurage</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪&nbsp;</strong></span>Gentle, flowing strokes to spread essential oils and induce calmness.</p>\r\n<h3>Petrissage</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪&nbsp;</strong></span>Kneading acupuncture and rolling massage therapy to relax physical pains and mental anxiety.</p>\r\n<h3>Friction</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Deep pressure and circular movements to focus on pain in common tight areas such as shoulders.</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"Essential Oil Diffuser: Spreading soothing scents during an aromatherapy massage session \" src=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/uploads/ckeditorimages/aromatherapy-essential-oils-diffuser.webp\" alt=\"An essential oils diffuser used in aromatherapy treatments\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></p>\r\n<h3>Percussion</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Rhythmic tapping to invigorate muscles through an multi sensory modern approach.</p>\r\n<h3>Stretching</h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪&nbsp;</strong></span>Gentle movements to soothe the body, improve flexibility and give you a really good massage!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Therapeutic Qualities of Essential Oils</h2>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Wondering which essential oils to choose? The three most popular choices in our body massage combination therapies are:</p>\r\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Lavender</h3>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Lavender is widely recognised for its calming and relaxing properties. It is often used to promote a relaxing environment, ease stress, and help with sleep problems.</p>\r\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Peppermint</h3>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Peppermint massage oil is known for its invigorating scent. Our therapist may apply it as part of a refreshing treatment or to help with headaches.</p>\r\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Tea Tree</h3>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #ff840c;\"><strong>➪ </strong></span>Tea tree essential oil has a distinct medicinal scent and is renowned for its potential antimicrobial properties. It is used to cleanse the air, support skin health, and address minor skin irritations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Aromatherapy at Home vs. in a Spa Environment</h2>\r\n<p>Experience the convenience and comfort of having your aromatherapy massage at home by booking our mobile service.</p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Our aromatherapy therapists can bring the full range of essential oils, from chamomile to lavender.</p>\r\n<p>No more commuting or waiting in spa lounges for the previous appointment to finish or massage therapist to arrive. Simply book one of our specialist therapists online and lie back to enjoy your professionally delivered aromatherapy massage in the comfort of your own space.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Book an Aromatherapy Massage in London</h3>\r\n<p>Book your mobile aromatherapy massage session with us today and let the skilled hands of one of our experienced specialist London therapists transport you away to a world of calm for an hour or two. Find your nearest trained therapist now:</p>\r\n<p>[[BOOKING]]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr class=\"separator\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">At Work?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #FC3C0B; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: #fc3c0b;\" title=\"Explore our Office Chair massage in London\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/office_massage\">Try Our Office Chair Massage</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt;\">or</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 5px; width: 60%; background-color: transparent;\" title=\"Explore all our massage treatments\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/treatments/treatments.html\">See All Treatments</a></p>', 1, 1, '2023-07-18 10:24:43', '2025-09-11 23:30:30', '<p>Enhance any massage with essential oils for benefits such as better sleep, increased vitality, or stress relief.</p>', '<p><a title=\"5-star rated therapists\" href=\"https://www.themassagerooms.com/Feedback/Feedback.html\">Top-rated Therapists</a></p>\r\n<p>Home and hotel visits</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Only &pound;59</strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 'Book Aromatherapy', 'https://www.themassagerooms.com/newbooking/newbooking.html', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Aromatherapy Massage | From £59 | TheMassageRooms', 'Relax with the soothing scents of an aromatherapy massage in your own space. Book a mobile therapist across London for a calming experience on demand.', 'aromatherapy-massage', 'Essential oil being poured during an aromatherapy massage in London', 'Aromatherapy Massage in London: Essential Oils, Much Needed Relaxation', NULL);
